flowchart TD
    Q["Incoming work (queue)"] --> CLS{"Assess risk"}
    CLS -->|low| LOW["Autonomous<br/>spec → plan → PR → notify"]
    CLS -->|medium / high| HI["Human gate<br/>analyze → plan → parity check"]
    HI --> CONF{"Human confirms?"}
    CONF -->|no| REVISE["Revise plan"]
    REVISE --> CONF
    CONF -->|yes| GO["Proceed to PR"]
    LOW --> DONE["Merge + record"]
    GO --> DONE
